[22/01/2019 00:52:09] <font color="#00ff00">"Ves otra cultura,</font>
[22/01/2019 00:52:09] <font color="#00ff00">otra forma de ver el mundo".</font>
[22/01/2019 00:52:12] <font color="#00ff00">"Y no solo la del Reino Unido,</font>
