[22/01/2019 15:47:17] <font color="#00ff00">"Saber y Ganar",</font>
[22/01/2019 15:47:30] <font color="#00ff00">un programa presentado</font>
[22/01/2019 15:47:30] <font color="#00ff00">por Jordi Hurtado.</font>
